✔ Zero dependency on on‑prem domain controllers
Cloud authentication continues even if:

AD is down
VPN is down
On‑prem network is down
AAD Connect server is offline


✔ Best compatibility with Conditional Access

MFA
Identity Protection
Sign‑in risk
Device compliance
Passwordless sign‑in
Zero Trust policies

All require cloud authentication → PHS enables this perfectly.

✔ Perfect for cloud-first strategy
PHS supports:

Microsoft 365
Azure
SaaS applications
Passwordless (FIDO2, WHfB)
Cloud Kerberos Trust


✔ Simpler than PTA and ADFS
No agents
No federation servers
No high-availability design
No certificate maintenance

